Elsie Okpocha, wife of popular comedian Bright Okpocha, popularly known as Basketmouth, has revealed she had three miscarriages. Elsie made this known in an Instagram post as she welcomed her third child. The mother of three said despite praying earnestly she had three miscarriages before her third child became successful. Her post read: “I prayed for this endlessly, I craved for it desperately. Even after two kids and three miscarriages. “God said it was time, his overtime time. It’s a new chapter. “God did finally hear one of my major prayers and I can’t thank him enough. “He has made me one of the happiest girls in the world. “This is my testimony, it’s a new chapter.”